This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image captioning. It also involves natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as entity recognition and caption generation, which suggests it could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. The use of deep learning models for vision and language tasks indicates that it could be classified under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves information retrieval tasks such as identifying landmarks and celebrities, which suggests it could also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
